folder: 66th Street (West) & West End Avenue, Manhattan, NY
text:
West 66th Street, west from West End Ave. to the North (Hudson) River. The elevated road bed shown at the water front is the West Side Vehicular Highway. Pier F. appears underneath same and across the N.Y. Central Railroad yards.

August 25, 1936.

W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.
